description: Are you looking for the best, freshest, most fantastic mini donuts on the move in Montana? Then The Rollin' Donut is the food truck for you! Made from the best ingredients and cooked up in quality canola oil, these mini donuts pack maximum flavor into every bite. Ready and waiting at all your favorite fairs and festivals, Montana's most amazing mini donuts are just what you've been looking for!
name: The Rollin' Donut
